text: "Parklife" is a 1994 song by Blur and is the title track to their third studio album Parklife. It went to number 10 in the United Kingdom, number 30 in Ireland, number 7 in Scotland and number 119 in Australia. ==Track listings== All music was composed by Albarn, Coxon, James and Rowntree.
